  "title": "Store Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us</strong><br />As part of Cotti Coffee Singapore’s expansion, we are looking for passionate and service-oriented Baristas and Senior Baristas to join our growing team. We are committed to delivering an outstanding customer experience and providing a supportive environment for your professional growth.</p><ul><li><strong>What You'll Do</strong></li><li>·      Resolve customer complaints                                </li><li><p>·      Maintain good relationships with customers      </p><p>·      Inventory control                                                 </p><p>·      Keep employees motivated                                   </p><p>·      Track inventory levels                                             </p><p>·      Store appearance and maintenance                     </p><p>·      Employee scheduling     <br /><br />.      Training staff                                       </p><p>·      Maintain store cleanliness                                    </p><p>·      Oversee pricing and handling control                 </p><p>·      Execute company marketing activities                 </p></li></ul><p><strong>What We're Looking For</strong></p><ul><li><p>At Least 3 years related experience</p></li><li><p>Available to work on weekends and public holidays</p></li><li><p>Reliable, punctual, and able to maintain consistent attendance</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Type</strong><br />Full-time </p><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li><p>Clear career progression pathways</p></li><li><p>Competitive compensation package</p></li><li><p>Professional coffee training and team support</p></li></ul>",
